summary: It’s 1:51am in the morning and all I can think about is how grateful I am to have exist in the same space and have known BTS....
body:
It’s 1:51am in the morning and all I can think about is how grateful I am to have exist in the same space and have known BTS. They are really a group of the most amazing, talented, passionate, kind-hearted artists EVER. 

They speak so truly and have so much love to give. Each album with a meaningful takeaway, with soulful lyrics; always reminding us to love ourselves - That there is no greater love than self-love. 

So thank you BTS, thank you for teaching us how to be the best version of ourselves. 

Quote-in-a-quote (quoting RM in #2018BTSFesta quoting another artist’s lyrics) because this hits me so hard. 

“행복이란 어디에도 없으며 어디에나 있구나"

Happiness is nowhere but everywhere
